  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A parallell group study comparing the effect of an education program with an education and
      training program for patients with COPD. 30 participants in each group. Participants
      self-select which group they wanted to be in. Main outcome is SGRQ (a HQoL for patients with
      COPD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
